flowchart LR
    INC[Incident]

    INC --> Q1{service down?}
    Q1 -->|yes| RB[check last deploy\nrollback if recent]
    Q1 -->|no| Q2{latency spike?}
    Q2 -->|yes| DB[check DB query plans\nand connection pool]
    Q2 -->|no| Q3{error rate spike?}
    Q3 -->|yes| LOG[check logs: 5xx patterns]
    Q3 -->|no| ESCALATE[escalate to senior eng]

    RB & DB & LOG --> RESOLVE[resolve]
    RESOLVE --> PIR[post-incident review]
